sequenceDiagram
    participant Sender
    participant Blockchain
    participant PublicChannel
    
    Sender->>Blockchain: Scan for recent activity<br/>(own transactions or latest blocks)
    Blockchain-->>Sender: Returns entropy source<br/>(tx hash or block hash)
    Sender->>Sender: Derive encryption key<br/>from entropy + recipient address
    Sender->>Sender: Encrypt message with XSalsa20-Poly1305
    Sender->>PublicChannel: Publish encrypted payload<br/>+ minimal metadata
